# Global Sales Dashboard Using Power BI

This project presents an interactive **Power BI** dashboard built using the **Global Superstore** sales dataset.  
The objective was to extract meaningful business insights by performing **data cleaning, transformation, and visualization**.

---

## ðŸ“Œ Project Overview
- **ETL Process:** Used **Power Query** to clean and transform raw data.
- **Analytics:** Created calculated measures and columns using **DAX** for enhanced analytics.
- **Dashboard Design:** Built an interactive dashboard with **cards, charts, slicers, and filters** for an intuitive user experience.
- **Insights:** Delivered actionable insights to help stakeholders make informed business decisions.

